[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> was <st data-num=\"06242\" class=\"\">twenty</st>-<st data-num=\"02568\" class=\"\">five</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">old</st> when he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">began to reign</st>, and he <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">reigned</st> <st data-num=\"06242\" class=\"\">twenty</st>-<st data-num=\"08672\" class=\"\">nine</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> His <st data-num=\"08034 0517\">mother</st><n id=\"2\" /> was <st data-num=\"029\" class=\"\">Abijah</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughter</st> of <st data-num=\"02148\" class=\"\">Zechariah</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"03477\" class=\"\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">approved</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">just</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestor</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">In the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st> of the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> of his <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">reign</st>, <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">opened</st> the <st data-num=\"01817\" class=\"\">doors</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> and <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">repaired</st> them.",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought in</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> and <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> and <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">assembled</st> them in the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">square</st> on the <st data-num=\"04217\" class=\"\">east side</st>.",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to them: \u201c<st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen to</st> me, you <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st>! <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrate</st> yourselves, so you can <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrate</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Remove</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">sanctuary</st> <st data-num=\"05079\" class=\"\">what is ceremonially unclean</st>.",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">fathers</st> <st data-num=\"04603\" class=\"\">were unfaithful</st>; they <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">what is evil</st> in the <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st> of<n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> and <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> him. They <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turned</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">away</st><n id=\"2\" /> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"04908\" class=\"\">dwelling place</st> and <st data-num=\"05414 06203\">rejected</st> him.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"01571 05462\">closed</st> the <st data-num=\"01817\" class=\"\">doors</st> of the <st data-num=\"0197\" class=\"\">temple porch</st> and <st data-num=\"03518\" class=\"\">put out</st> the <st data-num=\"05216\" class=\"\">lamps</st>; they did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">offer</st> <st data-num=\"07004\" class=\"\">incense</st> <st data-num=\"03808 05927\">or</st> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> in the <st data-num=\"06944\" class=\"\">sanctuary</st> of the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"07110\" class=\"\">angry</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> and <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">made</st> them an <st data-num=\"02113\" class=\"\">appalling object</st> of <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">horror</st> at which people <st data-num=\"08322\" class=\"\">hiss out</st> their <st data-num=\"08322\" class=\"\">scorn</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> can <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> with your own <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st>. ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">fathers</st> <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">died</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">violently</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and our <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>, <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st>, and <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> were <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">carried off</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because of</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>. ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> I <st data-num=\"05973 03824\">intend</st><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">make</st> a <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> with the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, so that he may <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">relent</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> his <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">raging</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "My <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>, do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> be <st data-num=\"07952\" class=\"\">negligent</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">chosen</st> you to <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stand</st> in his <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st>, to <st data-num=\"08334\" class=\"\">minister</st> to him,<n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> his <st data-num=\"08334\" class=\"\">ministers</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">offer sacrifices</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The following <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">prepared to carry out</st> the king\u2019s orders:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">From</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 06956\">Kohathites</st>: <st data-num=\"04287\" class=\"\">Mahath</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06022\" class=\"\">Amasai</st> and <st data-num=\"03100\" class=\"\">Joel</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariah</st>;<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 04847\">Merarites</st>: <st data-num=\"07027\" class=\"\">Kish</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05660\" class=\"\">Abdi</st> and <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"03094\" class=\"\">Jehallelel</st>;<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01649\" class=\"\">Gershonites</st>: <st data-num=\"03098\" class=\"\">Joah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02155\" class=\"\">Zimmah</st> and <st data-num=\"05731\" class=\"\">Eden</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"03098\" class=\"\">Joah</st>; </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> of <st data-num=\"0469\" class=\"\">Elizaphan</st>: <st data-num=\"08113\" class=\"\">Shimri</st> and <st data-num=\"03273\" class=\"\">Jeiel</st>;<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> of <st data-num=\"0623\" class=\"\">Asaph</st>: <st data-num=\"02148\" class=\"\">Zechariah</st> and <st data-num=\"04983\" class=\"\">Mattaniah</st>; </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> of <st data-num=\"01968\" class=\"\">Heman</st>: <st data-num=\"03171\" class=\"\">Jehiel</st> and <st data-num=\"08096\" class=\"\">Shimei</st>;<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04480\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> of <st data-num=\"03038\" class=\"\">Jeduthun</st>: <st data-num=\"08098\" class=\"\">Shemaiah</st> and <st data-num=\"05816\" class=\"\">Uzziel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">They <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">assembled</st> their <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st> and <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrated</st> themselves. Then they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went in</st> to <st data-num=\"02891\" class=\"\">purify</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>, just as the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> had <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">ordered</st>, in accordance with the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">word</st><n id=\"1\" /> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> then <st data-num=\"0935 06441\">entered</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> to <st data-num=\"02891\" class=\"\">purify</st> it; they <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">brought out</st> to the <st data-num=\"02691\" class=\"\">courtyard</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01964\" class=\"\">temple</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"02932 0834\">ceremonially unclean thing</st> they <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">discovered</st> <st data-num=\"01964 03068\">inside</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> <st data-num=\"06901\" class=\"\">took</st> them <st data-num=\"03318 02351\">out</st> to the <st data-num=\"06939\" class=\"\">Kidron</st> <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">Valley</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "On the <st data-num=\"0259\">first</st> day of the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st> they <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">began</st> <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrating</st>; by the <st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eighth</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of the <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st> they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">reached</st> the <st data-num=\"0197\" class=\"\">porch</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s temple.<n id=\"1\" /> For <st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eight</st> more <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> they <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrated</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>. On the <st data-num=\"08337 06240\">sixteenth</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st> they <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">were finished</st>. ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"0935 06441\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"02396\" class=\"\">Hezekiah</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: \u201cWe have <st data-num=\"02891\" class=\"\">purified</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, including the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> its <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">equipment</st>, and the <st data-num=\"07979\" class=\"\">table</st> for the <st data-num=\"04635\" class=\"\">Bread of the Presence</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> its <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">equipment</st>. ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "We have <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">prepared</st> and <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrated</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">items</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"0271\" class=\"\">Ahaz</st> <st data-num=\"02186\" class=\"\">removed</st> during his <st data-num=\"04438\" class=\"\">reign</st> when he <st data-num=\"04604\" class=\"\">acted unfaithfully</st>. <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">They</st> are <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">in front of</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"07925\" class=\"\">Early the next morning</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">assembled</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> and <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">went up</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>. ",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> <st data-num=\"06499\" class=\"\">bulls</st>, <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">rams</st>, <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> <st data-num=\"03532\" class=\"\">lambs</st>, and <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> <st data-num=\"06842 05795\">goats</st> as a <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin offering</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st>, the <st data-num=\"04720\" class=\"\">sanctuary</st>, <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> The king<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> of <st data-num=\"0175\" class=\"\">Aaron</st>, to <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offer burnt sacrifices</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"07819\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st> the <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">bulls</st>, and the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"06901\" class=\"\">took</st> the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> and <st data-num=\"02236\" class=\"\">splashed</st> it on the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>. Then they <st data-num=\"07819\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st> the <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">rams</st> and <st data-num=\"02236\" class=\"\">splashed</st> the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> on the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>; next they <st data-num=\"07819\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st> the <st data-num=\"03532\" class=\"\">lambs</st> and <st data-num=\"02236\" class=\"\">splashed</st> the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> on the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>. ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "Finally they <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">brought</st> the <st data-num=\"08163\" class=\"\">goats</st> for the <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin offering</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and the <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st>, and they <st data-num=\"05564\" class=\"\">placed</st> their <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> them.",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "Then the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"07819\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st> them. They <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">offered</st> their <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st> <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">as a sin offering</st> on the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> to <st data-num=\"03722\" class=\"\">make atonement</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> had <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">decreed</st><n id=\"1\" /> that the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st> and <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin offering</st> were for <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Hezekiah<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stationed</st> the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> with <st data-num=\"04700\" class=\"\">cymbals</st> and <st data-num=\"05035 03658\">stringed instruments</st> just as <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">prophet</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"05416\" class=\"\">Nathan</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> had <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">ordered</st>. (The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">actually</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">given</st> these <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">orders</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">through</st> his <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st>.) ",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">had</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> musical <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">instruments</st> and the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> had <st data-num=\"02689\" class=\"\">trumpets</st>. ",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02396\" class=\"\">Hezekiah</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">ordered</st> the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st> to be <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">offered</st> on the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>. <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">As</st> they <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">began</st> to offer the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st>, they also <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">began</st> to <st data-num=\"07892\" class=\"\">sing</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, accompanied by the <st data-num=\"02689\" class=\"\">trumpets</st> <st data-num=\"05921 03027\">and</st> the musical <st data-num=\"03627\">instruments</st> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st> <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st>, as the <st data-num=\"07891\" class=\"\">singers</st> <st data-num=\"07892\" class=\"\">sang</st> and the <st data-num=\"02689\" class=\"\">trumpeters</st> <st data-num=\"02690\" class=\"\">played</st>. <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">They</st> continued <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifice</st> was <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">completed</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When the <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st> were <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">completed</st>, the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him <st data-num=\"03766\" class=\"\">bowed down</st> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st>.",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> and the <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">told</st> the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> to <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">praise</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, using the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">psalms</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"0623\" class=\"\">Asaph</st> the <st data-num=\"02374\" class=\"\">prophet</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> So they <st data-num=\"05704 08057\">joyfully</st> <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">offered praise</st> and <st data-num=\"06915\" class=\"\">bowed down</st> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st>. ",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> <st data-num=\"06030 0559\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> you have <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">consecrated</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">yourselves</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">Come</st> and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st> and <st data-num=\"08426\" class=\"\">thank offerings</st><n id=\"2\" /> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>.\u201d So the <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st> and <st data-num=\"08426\" class=\"\">thank offerings</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whoever</st> <st data-num=\"05081 03820\">desired</st> to do so<n id=\"3\" /> brought <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st> <st data-num=\"01961 04557 05930 0834 0935\">brought</st> a <st data-num=\"03605 0428\">total</st> of <st data-num=\"07657\" class=\"\">70</st> <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">bulls</st>, <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">100</st> <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">rams</st>, and <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">200</st> <st data-num=\"03532\" class=\"\">lambs</st> as <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "and <st data-num=\"08337 03967\">600</st> <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">bulls</st> and <st data-num=\"07969 0505\">3,000</st> <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st><n id=\"1\" /> were <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrated</st>. ",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07535\" class=\"\">But</st> there <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">enough</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> to <st data-num=\"03201 06584\">skin</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">animals</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> so their <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>, the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st>, <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">helped</st> them <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> the <st data-num=\"04399\" class=\"\">work</st> was <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">finished</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> could <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrate</st> themselves. (The <st data-num=\"03588 03881\">Levites</st> had been more <st data-num=\"03477 03824\">conscientious</st> about <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrating</st> themselves than the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>.)<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "There was a <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">large number</st> of <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st>, <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">as well as</st> <st data-num=\"02459\" class=\"\">fat</st> from the <st data-num=\"08002\" class=\"\">peace offerings</st> and <st data-num=\"05262\" class=\"\">drink offerings</st> that accompanied the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st>. So the <st data-num=\"05656\" class=\"\">service</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st> was <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">reinstituted</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "35"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Chronicles",
    "chapter": "29",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03169\">Hezekiah</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"08055\">were happy</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> what <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> had <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">done</st><n id=\"1\" /> for <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">them</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">it</st> had <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">been done</st> <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">quickly</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "36"
  }
]